---
import VantageLayout from '../../../layouts/VantageLayout.astro';
import { brand } from '../../../data/vantage';
---

<VantageLayout title="Medical Weight Loss — VANTAGE Men's Health" description="Structured medical weight management with labs, GLP-1 evaluation, body composition support, and provider oversight.">

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="vt-section vt-section--dark mwl-hero">
	<div class="vt-container">
		<p class="vt-eyebrow">Medical Weight Loss</p>
		<h1>Weight management guided by labs, not willpower alone.</h1>
		<p class="vt-lead">Stubborn weight gain — especially around the midsection — can be driven by hormonal, metabolic, or inflammatory factors. A proper evaluation can help identify what's working against you.</p>
		<div class="vt-btn-row">
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--primary" href="/demos/hormone-trt/assessment">Take the Assessment &rarr;</a>
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--secondary" href="/demos/hormone-trt/book-consultation">Book Consultation</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- Beyond willpower -->
<section class="vt-section vt-section--charcoal mwl-beyond">
	<div class="vt-container mwl-beyond__layout">
		<div class="mwl-beyond__text">
			<p class="vt-eyebrow">Beyond Willpower</p>
			<h2>Why diets fail when your biology is working against you</h2>
			<p class="vt-lead">Most men who struggle with weight have already tried calorie restriction and exercise. When results plateau or reverse, the issue is often metabolic — not motivational.</p>
			<p>Low testosterone, insulin resistance, elevated cortisol, thyroid dysfunction, and poor sleep can all create a metabolic environment where fat storage is favored over fat loss. Medical weight management addresses these underlying factors.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="mwl-beyond__factors">
			<div class="mwl-beyond__factor">
				<h3>Hormonal imbalance</h3>
				<p>Low testosterone promotes visceral fat storage and reduces lean muscle mass.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-beyond__factor">
				<h3>Insulin resistance</h3>
				<p>Elevated insulin levels can make it nearly impossible to mobilize stored body fat.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-beyond__factor">
				<h3>Inflammation</h3>
				<p>Chronic low-grade inflammation can disrupt hunger signaling and metabolic function.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-beyond__factor">
				<h3>Sleep & stress</h3>
				<p>Cortisol dysregulation and poor sleep compound metabolic dysfunction.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- Pathway timeline -->
<section class="vt-section vt-section--slate mwl-pathway">
	<div class="vt-container">
		<div class="vt-section-header">
			<p class="vt-eyebrow">Your Pathway</p>
			<h2>A structured approach to medical weight management</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="mwl-pathway__timeline">
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step">
				<span class="mwl-pathway__marker">1</span>
				<div>
					<h3>Comprehensive metabolic assessment</h3>
					<p>Labs including fasting insulin, HbA1c, thyroid, hormones, and inflammatory markers to map your metabolic baseline.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step">
				<span class="mwl-pathway__marker">2</span>
				<div>
					<h3>Provider consultation</h3>
					<p>Review results, identify metabolic roadblocks, and discuss treatment options — including GLP-1 eligibility.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step">
				<span class="mwl-pathway__marker">3</span>
				<div>
					<h3>Personalized protocol</h3>
					<p>A treatment plan addressing your specific metabolic factors — may include medication, hormone optimization, or both.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="mwl-pathway__step">
				<span class="mwl-pathway__marker">4</span>
				<div>
					<h3>Regular monitoring & adjustment</h3>
					<p>Ongoing lab checks, body composition tracking, and protocol refinements to sustain progress.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- GLP-1 info -->
<section class="vt-section vt-section--charcoal mwl-glp1">
	<div class="vt-container mwl-glp1__layout">
		<div class="mwl-glp1__text">
			<p class="vt-eyebrow">GLP-1 Medications</p>
			<h2>GLP-1 receptor agonists: evaluation & oversight</h2>
			<p>GLP-1 medications (such as semaglutide and tirzepatide) may be appropriate for men who meet specific clinical criteria. At VANTAGE, eligibility is determined through labs and provider evaluation — not self-selection.</p>
			<p>These medications can support significant weight reduction when combined with metabolic optimization and provider oversight. They are not prescribed without proper evaluation, and ongoing monitoring is required.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="mwl-glp1__details">
			<div class="vt-card">
				<h3>Who may be a candidate</h3>
				<ul class="mwl-glp1__list">
					<li>BMI ≥ 30, or ≥ 27 with metabolic comorbidities</li>
					<li>Prior failed attempts with diet and exercise alone</li>
					<li>Lab-confirmed metabolic dysfunction</li>
					<li>No contraindications identified on evaluation</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="vt-card">
				<h3>What's included in oversight</h3>
				<ul class="mwl-glp1__list">
					<li>Dose titration guided by response and tolerability</li>
					<li>Regular lab monitoring (metabolic + hormonal panels)</li>
					<li>Provider check-ins at each dose adjustment</li>
					<li>Lean mass preservation strategies</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="vt-section vt-section--slate mwl-cta">
	<div class="vt-container mwl-cta__inner">
		<p class="vt-eyebrow">Get Started</p>
		<h2>Ready to understand what's driving your weight?</h2>
		<p class="vt-lead">A metabolic evaluation can reveal factors that willpower alone cannot overcome. Start with an assessment.</p>
		<div class="vt-btn-row">
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--primary" href="/demos/hormone-trt/assessment">Take the Assessment &rarr;</a>
			<a class="vt-btn vt-btn--secondary" href="/demos/hormone-trt/book-consultation">Book Consultation</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<!-- Disclaimer -->
<section class="vt-section vt-section--dark mwl-disclaimer">
	<div class="vt-container">
		<p class="mwl-disclaimer__text">{brand.disclaimer}</p>
	</div>
</section>

</VantageLayout>

<style>
.mwl-hero { padding-top: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem); padding-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem); }
.mwl-hero h1 { max-width: 700px; }
.mwl-hero .vt-lead { max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }

.mwl-beyond__layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
.mwl-beyond__text p:last-of-type { color: var(--vt-gray); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
.mwl-beyond__factors { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }
.mwl-beyond__factor { padding: 1.25rem; border: 1px solid var(--vt-border); border-radius: var(--vt-radius); }
.mwl-beyond__factor h3 { color: var(--vt-ivory); font-size: 0.95rem; }
.mwl-beyond__factor p { color: var(--vt-gray); font-size: 0.85rem; }

.mwl-pathway__timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; max-width: 640px; }
.mwl-pathway__step { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; align-items: flex-start; }
.mwl-pathway__marker { flex-shrink: 0; width: 2.25rem; height: 2.25rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--vt-bronze); color: var(--vt-graphite); font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.8rem; border-radius: 50%; }
.mwl-pathway__step h3 { color: var(--vt-ivory); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
.mwl-pathway__step p { color: var(--vt-gray); font-size: 0.875rem; }

.mwl-glp1__layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
.mwl-glp1__text p { color: var(--vt-gray); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
.mwl-glp1__details { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
.mwl-glp1__details h3 { color: var(--vt-ivory); }
.mwl-glp1__list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0.75rem 0 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
.mwl-glp1__list li { padding-left: 1rem; position: relative; color: var(--vt-gray); font-size: 0.85rem; }
.mwl-glp1__list li::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0.55em; width: 5px; height: 5px; background: var(--vt-bronze); border-radius: 50%; }

.mwl-cta__inner { text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin-inline: auto; }
.mwl-cta__inner .vt-lead { margin-inline: auto; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
.mwl-cta__inner .vt-btn-row { justify-content: center; }

.mwl-disclaimer__text { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--vt-gray); opacity: 0.6; font-style: italic; max-width: 640px; text-align: center; margin-inline: auto; }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
	.mwl-beyond__layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
	.mwl-glp1__layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
